		<h1 style="color: gold; font-size: 32px">Video Audition Registration Confirmation</h1>
		<p style="color: black; font-size:18px; text-align: left;">Dear __firstname,<br>
			<br> Congratulations on taking the first step to becoming a member of the Arsenal Drum and Bugle Corps! By submitting a video audition you are working to earn a callback to the March camp and in doing so are taking an important step towards securing yourself a contract in 2017!<br>
<br>
Please see the attached instructions for video auditions and please try to get your videos in to us as soon as possible. We are currently giving video assignments to our contracted members and callbacks, and we will give stronger consideration for membership to students who submit their videos early and complete assignment as well. The last day we will accept video auditions is March 1st.<br>
<br>
Please note that there is a $25 fee for auditioning by video, and that we will not review your video until the fee has been paid. We will send you an invoice upon receiving your video.<br>
<br>
We look forward to your submissions and to awarding callbacks for the March Camp!
			<br>
			<br>
			Warm regards,<br>
			<br>
			<strong>J. Spenser Lotz</strong>
			<br> Executive Director </p>
		<br>
		<p style="color: black; font-size:18px;">If you have any questions about this registration, or any concerns therein, please email <a href="mailto:contact@arsenalperformingarts.org" style="color: gold;text-decoration: none;">contact@arsenalperformingarts.org</a>
		</p>
